Features: remote control double garage, ducted heating, multiple split systems, security alarm, high ceilings, roller shutters, landscaped gardens, all of this plus too many other features to list. All set on a large allotment of approx 585sqm providing you with endless options as far as storage for the boat, caravan or trailer this home really is a must see. Ideally located within walking distance to transport, shops, parkland and schools.
